Create the `Context` for `do` elaboration from the given expected type of a `do` block. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.mkContext","kind":"def","line":636,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.mkContext","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L636-L641"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.enterFinally\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">enterFinally</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">resultType</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">k</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\">DoElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\">DoElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Prepare the context for elaborating the body of a `finally` block.\nThere is no support for `mut` vars, `break`, `continue` or `return` in a `finally` block.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.enterFinally","kind":"def","line":593,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.enterFinally","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L593-L599"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.withoutControl\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">withoutControl</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">k</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\">DoElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\">DoElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Prepare the context for elaborating the body of a `do` block that does not support `mut` vars,\n`break`, `continue` or `return`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.withoutControl","kind":"def","line":582,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.withoutControl","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L582-L591"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.enterLoopBody\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">enterLoopBody</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">breakCont </span><span class=\"fn\">continueCont</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\">DoElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">returnCont</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont\">ReturnCont</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">body</span> : <span c