 class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedReturnCont</span>.<span class=\"name\">default</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont\">ReturnCont</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.instInhabitedReturnCont.default","kind":"def","line":166,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.instInhabitedReturnCont.default","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L166-L166"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont.k\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">ReturnCont</span>.<span class=\"name\">k</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont\">ReturnCont</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\">DoElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The elaborator constructing a jump site to the return continuation,\ngiven some return value. The type of this return value determines the type of the jump expression;\nthis could very well be different than the `resultType` in case an intervening `match` as refined\n`resultType`. So `k` must *not* hardcode the type `resultType` into its definition; rather it\nshould infer the type of the return value argument.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont.k","kind":"def","line":165,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont.k","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L165-L165"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont.resultType\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">ReturnCont</span>.<span class=\"name\">resultType</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont\">ReturnCont</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont.resultType","kind":"def","line":157,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont.resultType","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L157-L157"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont.mk\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">ReturnCont</span>.<span class=\"name\">mk</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\">Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a></span>)</span> → <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont\">Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont.mk","kind":"ctor","line":156,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L156-L166"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">structure</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">ReturnCont</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont","kind":"structure","line":156,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.ReturnCont","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L156-L166"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElab\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">DoElab</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The type of elaborators for `do` block elements.\n\nIt is ``elabTerm `(do $e; $rest) = elabElem e dec``, where `elabElem e ·` is the elaborator for `do`\nelement `e`, and `dec` is the `DoElemCont` describing the elaboration of the rest of the block\n`rest`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElab","kind":"def","line":147,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.DoElab","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L147-L154"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.instInhabitedDoElemCont.default\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedDoElemCont</span>.<span class=\"name\">default</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont\">DoElemCont</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.instInhabitedDoElemCont.default","kind":"def","line":145,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.instInhabitedDoElemCont.default","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L145-L145"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.instInhabitedDoElemCont\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedDoElemCont</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont\">DoElemCont</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.instInhabitedDoElemCont","kind":"instance","line":145,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.instInhabitedDoElemCont","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L145-L145"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont.kind\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">DoElemCont</span>.<span class=\"name\">kind</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont\">DoElemCont</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind\">DoElemContKind</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Whether we are OK with generating the code of the continuation multiple times, e.g. in different\nbranches of a `match` or `if`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont.kind","kind":"def","line":144,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont.kind","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L144-L144"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont.k\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">DoElemCont</span>.<span class=\"name\">k</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont\">DoElemCont</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\">DoElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The continuation to elaborate the `rest` of the block. It assumes that the result of the `do`\nblock is bound to `resultName` with the correct type (that is, `resultType`, potentially refined\nby a dependent `match`).\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont.k","kind":"def","line":139,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont.k","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L139-L139"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont.resultType\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">DoElemCont</span>.<span class=\"name\">resultType</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont\">DoElemCont</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The type of the monadic result. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont.resultType","kind":"def","line":133,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont.resultType","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L133-L133"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont.resultName\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">DoElemCont</span>.<span class=\"name\">resultName</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont\">DoElemCont</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The name of the monadic result variable. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont.resultName","kind":"def","line":131,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont.resultName","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L131-L131"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont.mk\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">DoElemCont</span>.<span class=\"name\">mk</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Lean.Name</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\">Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind\">Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind</a> → <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont\">Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont</a></span></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont.mk","kind":"ctor","line":106,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L106-L145"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">structure</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">DoElemCont</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Elaboration of a `do` block `do $e; $rest`, results in a call\n``elabTerm `(do $e; $rest) = elabElem e dec``, where `elabElem e ·` is the elaborator for `do`\nelement `e`, and `dec` is the `DoElemCont` describing the elaboration of the rest of the block\n`rest`.\n\nIf the semantics of `e` resumes its continuation `rest`, its elaborator must bind its result to\n`resultName`, ensure that it has type `resultType` and then elaborate `rest` using `dec`.\n\nClearly, for term elements `e : m α`, the result has type `α`.\nMore subtly, for binding elements `let x := e` or `let x ← e`, the result has type `PUnit` and is\nunrelated to the type of the bound variable `x`.\n\nExamples:\n* `return` drops the continuation; `return x; pure ()` elaborates to `pure x`.\n* `let x ← e; rest x` elaborates to `e >>= fun x => rest x`.\n* `let x := 3; let y ← (let x ← e); rest x` elaborates to\n  `let x := 3; e >>= fun x_1 => let y := (); rest x`, which is immediately zeta-reduced to\n  `let x := 3; e >>= fun x_1 => rest x`.\n* `one; two` elaborates to `one >>= fun (_ : PUnit) => two`; it is an error if `one` does not have\n  type `PUnit`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont","kind":"structure","line":106,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemCont","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L106-L145"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.instInhabitedDoElemContKind.default\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedDoElemContKind</span>.<span class=\"name\">default</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind\">DoElemContKind</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.instInhabitedDoElemContKind.default","kind":"def","line":104,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.instInhabitedDoElemContKind.default","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L104-L104"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.instInhabitedDoElemContKind\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedDoElemContKind</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind\">DoElemContKind</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.instInhabitedDoElemContKind","kind":"instance","line":104,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.instInhabitedDoElemContKind","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L104-L104"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind.duplicable\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">DoElemContKind</span>.<span class=\"name\">duplicable</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind\">DoElemContKind</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind.duplicable","kind":"ctor","line":103,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind.duplicable","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L103-L103"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind.nonDuplicable\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">DoElemContKind</span>.<span class=\"name\">nonDuplicable</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind\">DoElemContKind</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind.nonDuplicable","kind":"ctor","line":102,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind.nonDuplicable","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L102-L102"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">DoElemContKind</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Whether the continuation of a `do` element is duplicable and if so whether it is just `pure r` for\nthe result variable `r`. Saying `nonDuplicable` is always safe; `duplicable` allows for more\noptimizations.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind","kind":"inductive","line":96,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.DoElemContKind","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L96-L104"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">DoElabM</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM","kind":"def","line":94,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.DoElabM","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L94-L94"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.Context.deadCode\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">deadCode</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.Context\">Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.CodeLiveness\">CodeLiveness</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Whether the current `do` element is dead code. `elabDoElem` will emit a warning if not `.alive`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.Context.deadCode","kind":"def","line":92,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.Context.deadCode","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L92-L92"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.Context.contInfo\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">contInfo</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.Context\">Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ContInfoRef\">ContInfoRef</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Information about `return`, `break` and `continue` continuations. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.Context.contInfo","kind":"def","line":88,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.Context.contInfo","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L88-L88"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.Context.doBlockResultType\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">doBlockResultType</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.Context\">Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The expected type of the current `do` block.\nThis can be different from `earlyReturnType` in `for` loop `do` blocks, for example.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Do.Context.doBlockResultType","kind":"def","line":86,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.Context.doBlockResultType","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Elab/Do/Basic.lean#L86-L86"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span